---
title: Smart Blueberry-Dressed  Chicken Tenders Salad with Almond Pralines
description: This summery salad is simple and tasty any time of the year! Mixed greens are tossed with a stellar blueberry vinaigrette, while pan-fried chicken brings a filling protein hit. Plus who can say no to sweet and crunchy almond pralines to top things off?!

